The paper proposes a method for predicting dependencies between multiple time series, which involves combining an RNN-based time series model with a Gaussian copula process output model with a low-rank covariance structure. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), statistics (cs.ST), information theory (cs.IT), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
